gs, this POK\u00e9MON is said to sing plaintively as it seeks what few others of its kind still remain."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"People have driven LAPRAS almost to the point of extinction. In the evenings, this POK\u00e9MON is said to sing plaintively as it seeks what few others of its kind still remain."},{"version":"emerald","text":"People have driven LAPRAS almost to the point of extinction. In the evenings, it is said to sing plaintively as it seeks what few others of its kind still remain."},{"version":"firered","text":"Its high intelligence enables it to understand human speech. It likes to ferry people on its back."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"A POK\u00e9MON that has been overhunted almost to extinction. It can ferry people on its back."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It loves crossing the sea with people and Pok\u00e9mon on its back. It understands human speech."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It loves crossing the sea with people and Pok\u00e9mon on its back. It understands human speech."},{"version":"platinum","text":"It loves crossing the sea with people and Pok\u00e9mon on its back. It understands human speech."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"They have gentle hearts. Because they rarely fight, many have been caught. Their number has dwindled."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It ferries people across the sea on its back. It may sing an enchanting cry if it is in a good mood."},{"version":"black","text":"It loves crossing the sea with people and Pok\u00e9mon on its back. It understands human speech."},{"version":"white","text":"It loves crossing the sea with people and Pok\u00e9mon on its back. It understands human speech."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Able to understand human speech and very intelligent, it loves to swim in the sea with people on its back."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Able to understand human speech and very intelligent, it loves to swim in the sea with people on its back."},{"version":"x","text":"They have gentle hearts. Because they rarely fight, many have been caught. Their number has dwindled."},{"version":"y","text":"Its high intelligence enables it to understand human speech. It likes to ferry people on its back."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"People have driven Lapras almost to the point of extinction. In the evenings, this Pok\u00e9mon is said to sing plaintively as it seeks what few others of its kind still remain."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"People have driven Lapras almost to the point of extinction. In the evenings, this Pok\u00e9mon is said to sing plaintively as it seeks what few others of its kind still remain."},{"version":"sun","text":"Its high intelligence enables it to comprehend human speech. When it\u2019s in a good mood, it sings in its beautiful voice."},{"version":"moon","text":"These Pok\u00e9mon were once near extinction due to poaching. Following protective regulations, there is now an overabundance of them."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It likes swimming around with people on its back. In the Alola region, it\u2019s an important means of transportation over water."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"They\u2019ve been so cherished that there\u2019s now an overabundance. The fish Pok\u00e9mon population has declined in waters with too many Lapras."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"A gentle soul that can understand human speech. It can ferry people across the sea on its back."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"A gentle soul that can understand human speech. It can ferry people across the sea on its back."},{"version":"sword","text":"A smart and kindhearted Pok\u00e9mon, it glides across the surface of the sea while its beautiful song echoes around it."},{"version":"shield","text":"Crossing icy seas is no issue for this cold-resistant Pok\u00e9mon. Its smooth skin is a little cool to the touch."}],"evo":{"name":"lapras","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":n